{"tid":2209912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"用光時頭像遭停課 擬海外升學  香島手足「學校冇得限制思想」","createTime":"2020-09-20T04:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T05:00:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f8775d6055290b49bb4d237d503c59158fdf67","tid":2209912,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=e3969ee9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI%2F&h=3432a5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TBOJOHWMPVBC3E6UXP36IVS2FI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n用光時頭像遭停課 擬海外升學 <br />\n香島手足「學校冇得限制思想」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香島中學中四生Gary（化名）因為在網上課堂頭像使用「光時」口號相片，遭校方勒令停課一周及建議考慮轉校。他近日透露，家人已為他申請休學，現積極考慮到海外繼續學業。Gary接受本報訪問時說，他在內地長大、中一才來港，但過去一年的經歷令他視香港為家，志願更由警察改為記者。<br />\n<br />\n遭校方勒令停學後，Gary至今心情仍未平復，但沒為當日的行為感後悔，。。。。。。。。。並建議他轉校或到海外升學，學校亦已經停用其所有網上學習賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RHFQmaN2O_WgQqxY17BWdisnxCw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TBFZDBHPKNDTXGLU3RXB6MD6BY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRHFQmaN2O_WgQqxY17BWdisnxCw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTBFZDBHPKNDTXGLU3RXB6MD6BY.jpg&h=86e33fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Gary以義務學生記者身份多次前往示威現場採訪，志向亦由警察轉為做記者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「做警察好羞愧」立志當記者<br />\n<br />\n倉卒離開校園，來不及與同學及師長道別，他說香島中學仍有不少好老師及好學生，只是學校高層以「紅色眼鏡」看待人和事，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。「雖然香島可以限制（學生）好多嘢，可以限制校內行為，但思想係冇得限制，所以希望大家可以堅持初衷，做自己覺得啱嘅事。」<br />\n<br />\nGary近日正備戰TOEFL試，去向未有定案，他樂意到海外留學見識世界，。。。。。。。。。。。。當日選擇香島中學，正因為其校園環境較易銜接。<br />\n<br />\n他形容2019年前的自己是「港豬」，但「抗暴之戰」不單令他思想有所轉變，。。。。。。。。。。。。。令他身為香港人而感動。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月至今，他由旁觀者變成記錄者，以義務學生記者身份多次走訪示威現場採訪。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。雖然家人政見與他不同，亦一直反對他當學生記者，但他相信這些責怪出於關心。<br />\n<br />\n「我以前係想做警察嘅，但（抗暴之戰）呢件事令我轉變太大，。。。。。。。。。。。。，他從中學會了冷靜處事。他知道記者人工低，但是不太介意，「養得起自己就得」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y7mEjw_UK00zhwxB-HcSXmL6pE8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R35SX545BRCSXCULFAW3YXQWIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy7mEjw_UK00zhwxB-HcSXmL6pE8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR35SX545BRCSXCULFAW3YXQWIQ.jpg&h=fa4659cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香島中學勒令Gary停課。資料圖片"},{"pid":"b5767c50631fe6a1fd8118a9fac91c705d8a42b2","tid":2209912,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"呢啲叫骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21732d6447bf325e5630dfbe97bd9cf47d6c087","tid":2209912,"uid":24814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:00:30.000Z","msg":"代五毛講：大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦同五毛講：屌你老母冚家鏟"}]}